      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="adhd-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <div class="intro-text">
          <p>
            Welcome to Allen Psychiatry in Provo, UT, your foremost healthcare
            provider dedicated to helping individuals with ADHD. We understand
            that ADHD can seem daunting, and we are here to provide
            comprehensive, personalized care that addresses all aspects of the
